---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="AI Automation for Engineering Teams" description="Woodhead Tech helps engineering teams cut manual ops and integrate AI tooling that actually works. Systems architecture and automation consulting.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="pill">
          <span class="pill-dot"></span>
          Systems Architecture &amp; AI Automation
        </div>
        <h1>
          Stop running your team<br />on manual work.
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          Woodhead Tech helps engineering teams cut ops toil and integrate AI into real workflows —
          not demos, not pilots. Systems that run in production.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Discovery Call →</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">See Services</a>
        </div>
        <div class="social-proof">
          <span>20+ years engineering</span>
          <span class="sep">·</span>
          <span>Rackspace · Amazon · Salesforce GovCloud</span>
          <span class="sep">·</span>
          <span>FedRAMP-cleared environments</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain points -->
  <section class="section pain-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">The problem</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">Your team is capable.<br />Your systems are holding them back.</h2>
      <div class="three-grid">
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="card-num">01</div>
          <h3>Manual toil stealing sprint capacity</h3>
          <p>Your engineers are spending hours on deploys, incident response, and runbooks that should be automated. That time belongs in your roadmap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="card-num">02</div>
          <h3>AI that doesn't connect to your systems</h3>
          <p>You've tried AI tools. They work in isolation but don't plug into your actual infrastructure. You need architecture, not another SaaS subscription.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="card-num">03</div>
          <h3>Architecture decisions made without expertise</h3>
          <p>Hiring a senior systems architect full-time costs $250K+. You need that expertise for specific decisions, not a permanent headcount.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I do -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <div class="split-text">
          <div class="section-eyebrow">What we do</div>
          <h2>Architecture that runs.<br />AI that earns its keep.</h2>
          <p>
            Woodhead Tech designs systems that automate real operational work — the CI/CD toil, the runbook
            theater, the alert noise — and integrates AI where it delivers measurable throughput,
            not where it looks good in a slide deck.
          </p>
          <p>
            Built on 20+ years of infrastructure engineering at Rackspace, Amazon AWS, and
            Salesforce GovCloud. FedRAMP-cleared environments. Go, Python, Bash. Terraform and
            Ansible. Kubernetes at scale.
          </p>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">About Woodhead Tech →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-list">
          <div class="stack-item">
            <div class="stack-label">Languages</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Go</span><span class="tag">Python</span><span class="tag">Bash</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-item">
            <div class="stack-label">Infrastructure</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Terraform</span><span class="tag">Ansible</span>
              <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span><span class="tag">Docker</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-item">
            <div class="stack-label">Cloud &amp; Compliance</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">AWS</span><span class="tag">GCP</span>
              <span class="tag">FedRAMP</span><span class="tag">GovCloud</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-item">
            <div class="stack-label">Observability</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Prometheus</span><span class="tag">Grafana</span>
              <span class="tag">Alertmanager</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services preview -->
  <section class="section surface-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Engagements</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">Three ways to work together.</h2>
      <div class="three-grid">
        <div class="card service-card">
          <div class="service-tier">Entry point</div>
          <h3>Discovery Audit</h3>
          <p>A deep-dive into your current systems. Walk away with a written report of automation opportunities and an AI integration roadmap.</p>
          <div class="service-price">From $2,000</div>
          <a href="/services#discovery" class="btn btn-outline service-btn">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card service-card service-featured">
          <div class="service-tier featured-tier">Most common</div>
          <h3>Project Engagement</h3>
          <p>Design and build one specific automation or AI integration — from architecture to production delivery.</p>
          <div class="service-price accent">$10,000–25,000</div>
          <a href="/services#project" class="btn btn-primary service-btn">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card service-card">
          <div class="service-tier">Ongoing</div>
          <h3>Advisory Retainer</h3>
          <p>Async architecture guidance and a monthly strategy call. Senior systems expertise on demand without the headcount.</p>
          <div class="service-price">$3,000/mo</div>
          <a href="/services#retainer" class="btn btn-outline service-btn">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof of work -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Proof of work</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">Built, not talked about.</h2>
      <div class="two-grid">
        <div class="card proof-card">
          <div class="proof-label">AI · Go · Alertmanager</div>
          <h3>AlertMind</h3>
          <p>AI-powered alert triage tool. Receives Alertmanager webhooks, enriches context, calls the Claude API for structured triage analysis, and posts to Discord — so on-call engineers arrive at an incident with a first-pass diagnosis already waiting.</p>
          <div class="proof-links">
            <a href="https://github.com/woodhead-tech/alertmind" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on GitHub →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card proof-card">
          <div class="proof-label">Ansible · Terraform · Self-hosted</div>
          <h3>ShopStack</h3>
          <p>Complete managed infrastructure for small businesses — email, file storage, database, reverse proxy, SSO, and monitoring — deployable on a $200 mini PC or AWS/GCP. Open source under MIT. Managed setup available.</p>
          <div class="proof-links">
            <a href="/shopstack" class="btn btn-outline">See ShopStack →</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/woodhead-tech/shopstack" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="homelab-cta">
        <span class="muted-text">20+ services, 5-node Proxmox cluster, full IaC — running in production.</span>
        <div class="paper-links">
          <a href="/homelab" class="btn btn-outline">Homelab architecture →</a>
          <a href="/sensor-to-alert" class="btn btn-outline">IoT automation white paper →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2>Ready to automate what's slowing you down?</h2>
        <p>Start with a 30-minute conversation. No pitch deck — just an honest look at where automation and AI can move the needle for your team.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Free Intro Call →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── Hero ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 7rem 0 6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% -20%, rgba(232, 88, 12, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .social-proof {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .sep { color: var(--border); opacity: 0.5; }

  /* ── Sections ── */
  .surface-section {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* ── Grids ── */
  .three-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .two-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── Pain cards ── */
  .pain-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

  .card-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .pain-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; }

  .pain-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ── Split layout ── */
  .split-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .split-text h2 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

  .split-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .stack-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .stack-item {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .stack-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.35rem; }

  .tag {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--dim);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ── Service cards ── */
  .service-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .service-featured {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent), 0 8px 32px rgba(232, 88, 12, 0.08);
  }

  .service-tier {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .featured-tier { color: var(--accent); }

  .service-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }

  .service-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); flex: 1; line-height: 1.65; }

  .service-price {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--dim);
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-price.accent { color: var(--accent); }

  .service-btn {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  /* ── Proof of work ── */
  .proof-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

  .proof-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .proof-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .proof-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; flex: 1; }

  .proof-links { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 0.25rem; }

  .proof-links .btn { font-size: 0.82rem; padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem; }

  .homelab-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .muted-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .paper-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .paper-links .btn { font-size: 0.85rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .homelab-cta .btn { font-size: 0.85rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cta-box {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-box h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

  .cta-box p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .three-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .two-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .hero { padding: 4rem 0 3.5rem; }
    .homelab-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
